# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Env / segredos. As chaves reais (service_role, EIA, brapi) vivem no painel do
# Netlify (escopo Functions), nunca no repo. .env.example fica versionado como
# modelo, sem valores.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Estado local do Netlify CLI
.netlify/

# Lockfile do Deno: artefato local do Netlify CLI (bootstrap de edge functions
# via Deno). O build de producao e `pnpm build` (Vite) e as Functions sao Node
# (node_bundler = esbuild, imports npm), entao o build NAO consome deno.lock. O
# lockfile que a Netlify usa e o pnpm-lock.yaml, esse sim versionado.
deno.lock

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
